content:
Remember: it will leave.
It is like a troublesome, noisy relative, 
Part of you,
Which cannot be disconnected,
But which fortunately,
Does not live with you. 
It will leave. 
Try not to kill it. 
Or escape. 
Just wait 
For it to leave. 
It will. 
Always. 

#NDVerse #Depression
